text: El Tepehuaje de Morelos is a town in the municipality of San Martín de Hidalgo in the state of Jalisco, Mexico. It has a population of 9,163.PueblosAmerica.com - El Tepehuaje de Morelos, San Martín Hidalgo, Jalisco The town was named after Mexican independence insurgent José María Morelos. ==References== ==External links== *El Tepehuaje de Morelos at PueblosAmerica.com Category:Populated places in Jalisco
